==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*Καπερναούμ / Kapernaoum / cap-er-nah-oom'
*Of Hebrew origin (probably [[כּפר]] {{HH|3723}} and [[נחוּם]] {{HH|5151}}); Capernaum (that is, Caphanachum), a place in [[Palestine]]: 

===Proper noun===
'''Καπερναούμ'''

# [[Capernaum]].  Capernaum = “village of comfort”

